room_title: Escape room "Pharaoh's Chamber" by Mind Trap Escape Rooms in Chicago
room_description: Entering an ancient tomb of King Tutankhamun, you are amazed at how unique and magical it looks. But little did you know that as soon as you stepped inside the tomb, a curse has befallen you... Now you only have an hour to find the sacred scarab and escape the room before the curse devours your soul!
